  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "An annotator with clinical training used the following three labels to annotate the free-text notes:",
    "We pre-train all of our models on the MIMIC-III dataset for a total of three epochs using either the MLM objective or Knowledge Distillation.",
    "We follow the same pre-processing used in Alsentzer et al. (2019) for MIMIC and use the BERT tokeniser from the Huggingface with a max length of 256 tokens.",
    "The details of the hyperparameters used for pre-training and fine-tuning our models are available in Tables 7 and 8.",
    "We evaluated the proposed models and the baselines on five datasets: MedNLI, i2b2-2010, i2b2-2012, i2b2-2014 and ICN."
  ],
